Epoll example
=============

This repository is simple example of non-blocking I/O event handling. It also
serves as a template for the assignment of Effective Software (ESW) course.

Build instructions:

    meson setup builddir
    cd builddir
    ninja

See the man pages for:
- epoll
- epoll_create1
- epoll_ctl
- epoll_wait
- timerfd_create
